text\": \"Mart\\u00edn reflected that the natural limit of the Hermes guide is tasks he triggers and the agent executes, not continuous sustained conversation; this marks a design boundary: the agent should operate more as a task orchestrator than a permanent interlocutor.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:29.178931+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:29.178931+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": null,\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"terreno\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": null,\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"736d5652-9a74-4dcd-a225-8a46583aef59\",\n      \"text\": \"Mart\\u00edn reflexiona que el l\\u00edmite natural de la gu\\u00eda Hermes son tareas que \\u00e9l dispara y el agente ejecuta, no la conversaci\\u00f3n continua sostenida. Esto marca un boundary de dise\\u00f1o: el agente deber\\u00eda operar m\\u00e1s como orquestador de tareas que como interlocutor permanente. | Involving: Mart\\u00edn\",\n      \"context\": \"descubrimiento-interaccion\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:29.178931+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"world\",\n      \"document_id\": \"d3b3a30e-2d52-4e60-be5c-fc23651fa7c2\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:29.178931+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"Hermes, Mart\\u00edn\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_d3b3a30e-2d52-4e60-be5c-fc23651fa7c2_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"terreno\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:47.469707+00:00\",\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"4ed149b6-a69f-4204-9ae1-d0785896e62c\",\n      \"text\": \"Mart\\u00edn observed that interacting with the Hermes guide via voice tires equally or more than by text; voice accelerates communicative throughput but does not reduce cognitive load per message.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:29.168931+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:29.168931+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": null,\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"terreno\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": null,\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"94d13eed-c07c-4a48-a25b-70c3b7e58b5d\",\n      \"text\": \"Mart\\u00edn observa que interactuar con la gu\\u00eda Hermes por voz cansa igual o m\\u00e1s que por texto; la voz acelera el throughput comunicativo pero no reduce la carga cognitiva por mensaje. | Involving: Mart\\u00edn\",\n      \"context\": \"descubrimiento-interaccion\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:29.168931+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"world\",\n      \"document_id\": \"d3b3a30e-2d52-4e60-be5c-fc23651fa7c2\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:29.168931+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"Hermes, Mart\\u00edn\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_d3b3a30e-2d52-4e60-be5c-fc23651fa7c2_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"terreno\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:31:47.469707