null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"9c0ee594-4663-4646-907e-b442d71c0b77\",\n      \"text\": \"Kair\\u00f3s is the governance framework for the kirlts/personal repository, operating with two poles: Terreno (facts, Kratos) and Mito (strategic action, Khaos). It establishes asymmetric dependency (Mito cites Terreno), prohibits autonomous modification of the KB (\\u00a7R1), and has separate authorization domains.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:13.648443+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:13.648443+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": null,\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"kairos-framework\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": null,\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"c6ec009a-ae73-4ccf-8e81-4f942455e835\",\n      \"text\": \"Kair\\u00f3s es el framework de gobernanza del repositorio kirlts/personal, operando con dos polos: Terreno (hechos, Kratos) y Mito (acci\\u00f3n estrat\\u00e9gica, Khaos). Establece dependencia asim\\u00e9trica (Mito cita a Terreno), prohibici\\u00f3n de modificaci\\u00f3n aut\\u00f3noma de la KB (\\u00a7R1) y dominios de autorizaci\\u00f3n separados.\",\n      \"context\": \"gobernanza Kair\\u00f3s\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:13.648443+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"world\",\n      \"document_id\": \"e5bd51ad-4b30-4bb2-89cb-4ca379142ef0\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:13.648443+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"Kair\\u00f3s, Terreno, Mito, Kratos, kirlts/personal, Khaos, KB\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_e5bd51ad-4b30-4bb2-89cb-4ca379142ef0_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"kairos-framework\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:58.443352+00:00\",\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"58217a00-d249-43dc-8b51-867e0839dde4\",\n      \"text\": \"Tono unificado para todos los canales de Hermes: espa\\u00f1ol neutro, conciso, sin emojis, sin lenguaje corporativo. Heredado del orquestador default. Diferenciaci\\u00f3n futura posible pero no necesaria ahora.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:12.639404+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:12.639404+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": null,\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"tone\",\n        \"pending\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": null,\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"bf2f96bf-2704-402c-8d4a-54ec15167740\",\n      \"text\": \"Tono unificado para todos los canales de Hermes: espa\\u00f1ol neutro, conciso, sin emojis, sin lenguaje corporativo. Heredado del orquestador default. Diferenciaci\\u00f3n futura posible pero no necesaria ahora.\",\n      \"context\": \"preferencia de tono\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:12.639404+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"world\",\n      \"document_id\": \"a4bde4c6-6d64-4a44-8b13-d5661a2e6419\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:12.639404+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"orquestador default, Hermes\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_a4bde4c6-6d64-4a44-8b13-d5661a2e6419_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"tone\",\n        \"pending\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-28T21:42:01.486708+00:00\",\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"35399e49-3e37-4184-b87b-09007933c7ac\",\n      \"text\": \"Mart\\u00edn designed the Hermes personal profile with a personal-buffer staging area for pending content, a personal-profile canonical bank for curated knowledge, on-demand review sessions, Kilo CLI + compile.py integration, a lax inclusion policy, and no code/infrastructure modification rights.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:11.636316+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:11.636316+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": null,\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"buffer-design\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": null,\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b859cea8-b52d-4f34-82bb-eec051b8d469\",\n      \"text\": \"Mart\\u00edn defini\\u00f3 el dise\\u00f1o del perfil personal de Hermes: buffer de staging (personal-buffer) donde todo contenido con carga sem\\u00e1ntica entra en estado pending; banco can\\u00f3nico (personal-profile) solo con conocimiento curado; sesiones de revisi\\u00f3n a demanda; integraci\\u00f3n a la KB v\\u00eda Kilo CLI + compile.py; pol\\u00edtica laxa (ante la duda, entra); el perfil personal no puede modificar c\\u00f3digo ni infraestructura. | Involving: Mart\\u00edn (usuario)\",\n      \"context\": \"dise\\u00f1o del sistema\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:11.636316+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"world\",\n      \"document_id\": \"6d9157af-3056-4fd1-bfc5-94e4b665b9c3\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:11.636316+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"Kilo CLI, compile.py, Hermes, KB, personal-profile, Mart\\u00edn, personal-buffer\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_6d9157af-3056-4fd1-bfc5-94e4b665b9c3_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"buffer-design\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-28T21:41:52.585783+00:00\",\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 34,\n  \"limit\": 1000,\n  \"offset\": 0\n}", "structuredContent": {"result": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"99caeacb-21e8-4841-8840-6e565f3c488b\",\n      \"text\": \"Diagnosed a routing failure and documented lessons (voice vs text same cognitive load, natural agent limit as task orchestrator, failure due to lack of programmatic enforcement). Decisions include bidirectional protocol for Personal channel, unified tone, on-demand review sessions, and gateway pre-processor as solution.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00.030000+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-30T02:28:52.445751+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00.030000+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_end\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00.030000+00:00\",\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": null,\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"2026-06-30\",\n        \"daily-summary\",\n        \"personal-buffer\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": null,\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"11b9deb4-4713-471d-9dab-e3cbf4b04551\",\n      \"text\": \"Diagn\\u00f3stico de falla de ruteo documentado con lecciones (voz vs texto misma carga cognitiva, l\\u00edmite natural del agente como orquestador de tareas, fallo por falta de enforcement program\\u00e1tico). Decisiones: protocolo bidireccional canal Personal, tono unificado, sesiones de revisi\\u00f3n a demanda, gateway pre-processor como soluci\\u00f3n. | When: 2026-06-29\",\n      \"context\": \"general\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00.030000+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"experience\",\n      \"document_id\": \"44d77983-5308-4478-989e-f01a5ffc5adc\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-30T02:28:52.445751+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00.030000+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_end\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00.030000+00:00\",\n      \"entities\": \"canal Personal, falla de ruteo, gateway pre-processor\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_44d77983-5308-4478-989e-f01a5ffc5adc_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"2026-06-30\",\n        \"daily-summary\",\n        \"personal-buffer\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-30T02:29:42.659149+00:00\",\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"a11e0a7d-d6dc-4684-a686-40bb27308ff9\",\n      \"text\": \"Cloned the toolset to /opt/toolset.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00.020000+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-30T02:28:52.435751+00:00\"