: el algoritmo de ruteo es texto en system prompt que compite con otras instrucciones, sin enforcement program\\u00e1tico.\",\n      \"context\": \"diagn\\u00f3stico-de-ruteo\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:51:42.202689+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"world\",\n      \"document_id\": \"78fe3108-090c-410a-99a3-8f8369ecf2ce\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:51:42.202689+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_78fe3108-090c-410a-99a3-8f8369ecf2ce_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"diagnostico-ruteo\",\n        \"pending\",\n        \"feedback\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:52:26.602223+00:00\",\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"4a2e24cd-190e-4229-84d3-dfac7b42d83e\",\n      \"text\": \"Documento completo de diagn\\u00f3stico de falla de ruteo en grupo Personal escrito en ~/hermes-routing-root-cause.md | When: 2026-06-29 | Involving: Buffer de entrada para perfil personal (el agente de IA) | Diagnosticar y documentar la falla de ruteo en grupo Personal\",\n      \"context\": \"diagn\\u00f3stico-de-ruteo\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:51:42.192689+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"experience\",\n      \"document_id\": \"78fe3108-090c-410a-99a3-8f8369ecf2ce\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:51:42.192689+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": \"2026-06-29T00:51:42.192689+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_end\": \"2026-06-29T00:51:42.192689+00:00\",\n      \"entities\": \"~hermes-routing-root-cause.md, Personal\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_78fe3108-090c-410a-99a3-8f8369ecf2ce_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"diagnostico-ruteo\",\n        \"pending\",\n        \"feedback\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:52:26.602223+00:00\",\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"e74e617f-fb7e-4465-b5ec-882f900732be\",\n      \"text\": \"The SOUL.md routing algorithm must be executed without exception in every group message; it should not assume DM.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:48:18.911249+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:48:18.911249+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": null,\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"feedback\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": null,\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"6d347598-4e1a-4c12-a736-f9ecf72adc5c\",\n      \"text\": \"Lecci\\u00f3n: el algoritmo de ruteo del SOUL.md debe ejecutarse sin excepci\\u00f3n en cada mensaje de grupo, no asumir DM. | Debido al error anterior\",\n      \"context\": \"feedback-de-ruteo\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:48:18.911249+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"world\",\n      \"document_id\": \"2b5be9da-c37a-4b2b-abd7-56fc87eaa502\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:48:18.911249+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"SOUL.md, algoritmo de ruteo\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_2b5be9da-c37a-4b2b-abd7-56fc87eaa502_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"feedback\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:48:45.473806+00:00\",\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"c171d775-503f-49bd-b71f-f70b3f38f44e\",\n      \"text\": \"Hermes failed to execute the multi-group routing algorithm correctly in the Personal group (120363429377303869@g.us); instead of loading personal-profile, personal-buffer, and reading SOUL.md, it executed recall(bank='hermes') (DM route). The user detected and reported the error on June 29, 2026.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:48:18.901249+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_end\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00+00:00\",\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": null,\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"feedback\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": null,\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ff424391-28d5-4383-b66c-7f82e7e5cdaa\",\n      \"text\": \"Hermes fall\\u00f3 en ejecutar el algoritmo de ruteo multi-grupo correctamente en el grupo Personal (120363429377303869@g.us): en el primer mensaje ejecut\\u00f3 recall(bank='hermes') (ruta DM) en lugar de cargar personal-profile, personal-buffer y leer SOUL.md del perfil. El usuario detect\\u00f3 y report\\u00f3 el error. | When: Lunes, 29 de junio de 2026 | Involving: Hermes (agente), usuario\",\n      \"context\": \"feedback-de-ruteo\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"world\",\n      \"document_id\": \"2b5be9da-c37a-4b2b-abd7-56fc87eaa502\",\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:48:18.901249+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_end\": \"2026-06-29T00:00:00+00:00\",\n      \"entities\": \"SOUL.md, personal-buffer, grupo Personal, personal-profile, usuario, Hermes\",\n      \"chunk_id\": \"personal-buffer_2b5be9da-c37a-4b2b-abd7-56fc87eaa502_0\",\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"feedback\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:48:45.473806+00:00\",\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"699db4a9-9bd3-4079-8ff8-c8368333d855\",\n      \"text\": \"Protocolo bidireccional del canal Personal: (1) INPUT - todo lo que Mart\\u00edn dice va autom\\u00e1ticamente a personal-buffer con tag pending. (2) OUTPUT - cuando Mart\\u00edn pregunta, Hermes debe consultar personal-buffer y personal-profile (Terreno/Mito) antes de responder. La Knowledge Base es el contexto que da valor a la conversaci\\u00f3n. Sin aislamiento.\",\n      \"context\": \"\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-06-29T00:33:27.720898+00:00\",\n      \"fact_type\": \"observation\",\n      \"document_id\": null,\n      \"mentioned_at\": \"2026-06-29T00:33:27.720898+00:00\",\n      \"occurred_start\": null,\n      \"occurred_end\": null,\n      \"entities\": \"\",\n      \"chunk_id\": null,\n      \"proof_count\": 1,\n      \"tags\": [\n        \"pending\",\n        \"terreno\"\n      ],\n      \"consolidated_at\": null,\n      \"consolidation_failed_at\": null,\n      \"state\": \"valid\",\n      \"invalidation_reason\": null,\n      \"invalidated_at\": null,\n      \"edited_at\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"3e28afdd-296c-4a9b-b438-069175286c6d\",\n      \"text\": \"Protocolo bidireccional del canal Personal: (1) INPUT - todo lo que Mart\\u00edn dice va autom\\u00e1ticamente a personal-buffer con tag pending. (2) OUTPUT - cuando Mart\\u00edn pregunta, Hermes debe consultar personal-buffer y personal-profile (Terreno/Mito) antes de 